profile.bio:
Founder/CEO for Evident.io, long time infosec professional fighting the good fight at companies like Adobe, Ingenuity, PGP, Ticketmaster, Motorola, and more...

BBQ Afficionado, car geek, gamer, father, 110% nerd.
